    "ts": "2026-04-30T11:04:52+00:00",
    "headline": "Carrier Global (NYSE:CARR) Posts Better-Than-Expected Sales In Q1 CY2026",
    "summary": "Heating, ventilation, air conditioning, and refrigeration company Carrier Global (NYSE:CARR) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q1 CY2026, with sales up 2.4% year on year to $5.34 billion. The company expects the full year’s revenue to be around $22 billion, close to analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.57 per share was 12.1% above analysts’ consensus estimates.",
